3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper involves interpolation of fractional samples, which can be considered as a form of signal processing, a sub-topic of information retrieval. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a machine learning approach using CNNs for video coding.
